sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant RP as ReferencePrecalculator
    participant DIS as Dispatcher
    participant EXP as Dispatch Exposure View
    participant BF as Bridge-Facing Adapter
    participant RS as Read-Side / Receiver Boundary

    RP-->>DIS: TDispatchAccessRef
